var book = {
	"name": "Hebrews",
	"numChapters": 13,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>In the past God spoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29965A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29965A\"></sup> to our ancestors through the prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29965B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29965B\"></sup> at many times and in various ways,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29965C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29965C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>but in these last days<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29966D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29966D\"></sup> he has spoken to us by his Son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29966E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29966E\"></sup> whom he appointed heir<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29966F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29966F\"></sup> of all things, and through whom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29966G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29966G\"></sup> also he made the universe.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29966H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29966H\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The Son is the radiance of God’s glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29967I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29967I\"></sup> and the exact representation of his being,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29967J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29967J\"></sup> sustaining all things<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29967K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29967K\"></sup> by his powerful word. After he had provided purification for sins,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29967L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29967L\"></sup> he sat down at the right hand of the Majesty in heaven.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29967M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29967M\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>So he became as much superior to the angels as the name he has inherited is superior to theirs.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29968N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29968N\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For to which of the angels did God ever say,“You are my Son;today I have become your Father”?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29969O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29969O\"></sup>Or again,“I will be his Father,and he will be my Son”?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29969P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29969P\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And again, when God brings his firstborn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29970Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29970Q\"></sup> into the world,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29970R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29970R\"></sup> he says,“Let all God’s angels worship him.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29970S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29970S\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>In speaking of the angels he says,“He makes his angels spirits,and his servants flames of fire.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29971T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29971T\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But about the Son he says,“Your throne, O God, will last for ever and ever;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29972U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29972U\"></sup>a scepter of justice will be the scepter of your kingdom.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>You have loved righteousness and hated wickedness;therefore God, your God, has set you above your companions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29973V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29973V\"></sup>by anointing you with the oil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29973W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29973W\"></sup> of joy.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29973X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29973X\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He also says,“In the beginning, Lord, you laid the foundations of the earth,and the heavens are the work of your hands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29974Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29974Y\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They will perish, but you remain;they will all wear out like a garment.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29975Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29975Z\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>You will roll them up like a robe;like a garment they will be changed.But you remain the same,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29976AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29976AA\"></sup>and your years will never end.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29976AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29976AB\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>To which of the angels did God ever say,“Sit at my right hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29977AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29977AC\"></sup>until I make your enemiesa footstool<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29977AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29977AD\"></sup> for your feet”?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29977AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29977AE\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Are not all angels ministering spirits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29978AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29978AF\"></sup> sent to serve those who will inherit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29978AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29978AG\"></sup> salvation?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29978AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29978AH\"></sup>"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>We must pay the most careful attention, therefore, to what we have heard, so that we do not drift away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29979A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29979A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For since the message spoken<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29980B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29980B\"></sup> through angels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29980C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29980C\"></sup> was binding, and every violation and disobedience received its just punishment,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29980D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29980D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>how shall we escape if we ignore so great a salvation?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29981E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29981E\"></sup> This salvation, which was first announced by the Lord,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29981F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29981F\"></sup> was confirmed to us by those who heard him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29981G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29981G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>God also testified to it by signs, wonders and various miracles,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29982H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29982H\"></sup> and by gifts of the Holy Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29982I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29982I\"></sup> distributed according to his will.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29982J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29982J\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>It is not to angels that he has subjected the world to come, about which we are speaking.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But there is a place where someone<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29984K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29984K\"></sup> has testified:“What is mankind that you are mindful of them,a son of man that you care for him?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29984L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29984L\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>You made them a little lower than the angels;you crowned them with glory and honor",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>and put everything under their feet.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29986M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29986M\"></sup>In putting everything under them, God left nothing that is not subject to them. Yet at present we do not see everything subject to them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But we do see Jesus, who was made lower than the angels for a little while, now crowned with glory and honor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29987N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29987N\"></sup> because he suffered death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29987O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29987O\"></sup> so that by the grace of God he might taste death for everyone.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29987P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29987P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>In bringing many sons and daughters to glory, it was fitting that God, for whom and through whom everything exists,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29988Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29988Q\"></sup> should make the pioneer of their salvation perfect through what he suffered.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29988R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29988R\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Both the one who makes people holy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29989S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29989S\"></sup> and those who are made holy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29989T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29989T\"></sup> are of the same family. So Jesus is not ashamed to call them brothers and sisters.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29989U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29989U\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He says,“I will declare your name to my brothers and sisters;in the assembly I will sing your praises.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29990V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29990V\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And again,“I will put my trust in him.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29991W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29991W\"></sup>And again he says,“Here am I, and the children God has given me.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29991X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29991X\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Since the children have flesh and blood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29992Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29992Y\"></sup> he too shared in their humanity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29992Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29992Z\"></sup> so that by his death he might break the power<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29992AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29992AA\"></sup> of him who holds the power of death—that is, the devil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29992AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29992AB\"></sup>—",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and free those who all their lives were held in slavery by their fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29993AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29993AC\"></sup> of death.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For surely it is not angels he helps, but Abraham’s descendants.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29994AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29994AD\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For this reason he had to be made like them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29995AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29995AE\"></sup> fully human in every way, in order that he might become a merciful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29995AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29995AF\"></sup> and faithful high priest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29995AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29995AG\"></sup> in service to God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29995AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29995AH\"></sup> and that he might make atonement for the sins of the people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29995AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29995AI\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Because he himself suffered when he was tempted, he is able to help those who are being tempted.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29996AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29996AJ\"></sup>"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Therefore, holy brothers and sisters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29997A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29997A\"></sup> who share in the heavenly calling,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29997B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29997B\"></sup> fix your thoughts on Jesus, whom we acknowledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29997C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29997C\"></sup> as our apostle and high priest.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29997D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29997D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He was faithful to the one who appointed him, just as Moses was faithful in all God’s house.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29998E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29998E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Jesus has been found worthy of greater honor than Moses,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29999F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29999F\"></sup> just as the builder of a house has greater honor than the house itself.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For every house is built by someone, but God is the builder of everything.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30000G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30000G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Moses was faithful as a servant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30001H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30001H\"></sup> in all God’s house,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30001I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30001I\"></sup> bearing witness to what would be spoken by God in the future.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But Christ is faithful as the Son<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30002J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30002J\"></sup> over God’s house. And we are his house,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30002K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30002K\"></sup> if indeed we hold firmly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30002L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30002L\"></sup> to our confidence and the hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30002M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30002M\"></sup> in which we glory.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So, as the Holy Spirit says:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30003N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30003N\"></sup>“Today, if you hear his voice,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>do not harden your hearts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30004O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30004O\"></sup>as you did in the rebellion,during the time of testing in the wilderness,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>where your ancestors tested and tried me,though for forty years they saw what I did.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30005P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30005P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>That is why I was angry with that generation;I said, ‘Their hearts are always going astray,and they have not known my ways.’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So I declared on oath in my anger,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30007Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30007Q\"></sup>‘They shall never enter my rest.’ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30007R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30007R\"></sup>”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30007S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30007S\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>See to it, brothers and sisters, that none of you has a sinful, unbelieving heart that turns away from the living God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30008T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30008T\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But encourage one another daily,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30009U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30009U\"></sup> as long as it is called “Today,” so that none of you may be hardened by sin’s deceitfulness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30009V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30009V\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>We have come to share in Christ, if indeed we hold<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30010W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30010W\"></sup> our original conviction firmly to the very end.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30010X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30010X\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>As has just been said:“Today, if you hear his voice,do not harden your heartsas you did in the rebellion.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30011Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30011Y\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Who were they who heard and rebelled? Were they not all those Moses led out of Egypt?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30012Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30012Z\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And with whom was he angry for forty years? Was it not with those who sinned, whose bodies perished in the wilderness?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30013AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30013AA\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And to whom did God swear that they would never enter his rest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30014AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30014AB\"></sup> if not to those who disobeyed?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30014AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30014AC\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>So we see that they were not able to enter, because of their unbelief.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30015AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30015AD\"></sup>"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Therefore, since the promise of entering his rest still stands, let us be careful that none of you be found to have fallen short of it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30016A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30016A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For we also have had the good news proclaimed to us, just as they did; but the message they heard was of no value to them, because they did not share the faith of those who obeyed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30017B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30017B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Now we who have believed enter that rest, just as God has said,“So I declared on oath in my anger,‘They shall never enter my rest.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30018C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30018C\"></sup>And yet his works have been finished since the creation of the world.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For somewhere he has spoken about the seventh day in these words: “On the seventh day God rested from all his works.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30019D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30019D\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And again in the passage above he says, “They shall never enter my rest.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30020E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30020E\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore since it still remains for some to enter that rest, and since those who formerly had the good news proclaimed to them did not go in because of their disobedience,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30021F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30021F\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>God again set a certain day, calling it “Today.” This he did when a long time later he spoke through David, as in the passage already quoted:“Today, if you hear his voice,do not harden your hearts.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30022G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30022G\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For if Joshua had given them rest,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30023H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30023H\"></sup> God would not have spoken<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30023I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30023I\"></sup> later about another day.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>There remains, then, a Sabbath-rest for the people of God;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>for anyone who enters God’s rest also rests from their works,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30025J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30025J\"></sup> just as God did from his.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30025K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30025K\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Let us, therefore, make every effort to enter that rest, so that no one will perish by following their example of disobedience.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30026L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30026L\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For the word of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30027M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30027M\"></sup> is alive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30027N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30027N\"></sup> and active.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30027O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30027O\"></sup> Sharper than any double-edged sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30027P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30027P\"></sup> it penetrates even to dividing soul and spirit, joints and marrow; it judges the thoughts and attitudes of the heart.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30027Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30027Q\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Nothing in all creation is hidden from God’s sight.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30028R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30028R\"></sup> Everything is uncovered and laid bare before the eyes of him to whom we must give account.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore, since we have a great high priest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30029S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30029S\"></sup> who has ascended into heaven,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30029T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30029T\"></sup> Jesus the Son of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30029U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30029U\"></sup> let us hold firmly to the faith we profess.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30029V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30029V\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For we do not have a high priest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30030W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30030W\"></sup> who is unable to empathize with our weaknesses, but we have one who has been tempted in every way, just as we are<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30030X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30030X\"></sup>—yet he did not sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30030Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30030Y\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Let us then approach<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30031Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30031Z\"></sup> God’s throne of grace with confidence,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30031AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30031AA\"></sup> so that we may receive mercy and find grace to help us in our time of need."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>Every high priest is selected from among the people and is appointed to represent the people in matters related to God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30032A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30032A\"></sup> to offer gifts and sacrifices<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30032B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30032B\"></sup> for sins.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30032C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30032C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He is able to deal gently with those who are ignorant and are going astray,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30033D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30033D\"></sup> since he himself is subject to weakness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30033E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30033E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>This is why he has to offer sacrifices for his own sins, as well as for the sins of the people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30034F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30034F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And no one takes this honor on himself, but he receives it when called by God, just as Aaron was.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30035G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30035G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>In the same way, Christ did not take on himself the glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30036H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30036H\"></sup> of becoming a high priest.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30036I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30036I\"></sup> But God said<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30036J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30036J\"></sup> to him,“You are my Son;today I have become your Father.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30036K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30036K\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And he says in another place,“You are a priest forever,in the order of Melchizedek.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30037L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30037L\"></sup>”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30037M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30037M\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>During the days of Jesus’ life on earth, he offered up prayers and petitions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30038N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30038N\"></sup> with fervent cries and tears<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30038O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30038O\"></sup> to the one who could save him from death, and he was heard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30038P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30038P\"></sup> because of his reverent submission.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30038Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30038Q\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Son<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30039R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30039R\"></sup> though he was, he learned obedience from what he suffered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30039S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30039S\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and, once made perfect,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30040T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30040T\"></sup> he became the source of eternal salvation for all who obey him",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and was designated by God to be high priest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30041U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30041U\"></sup> in the order of Melchizedek.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30041V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30041V\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>We have much to say about this, but it is hard to make it clear to you because you no longer try to understand.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>In fact, though by this time you ought to be teachers, you need someone to teach you the elementary truths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30043X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30043X\"></sup> of God’s word all over again. You need milk, not solid food!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30043Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30043Y\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Anyone who lives on milk, being still an infant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30044Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30044Z\"></sup> is not acquainted with the teaching about righteousness.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But solid food is for the mature,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30045AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30045AA\"></sup> who by constant use have trained themselves to distinguish good from evil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30045AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30045AB\"></sup>"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>Therefore let us move beyond<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30046A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30046A\"></sup> the elementary teachings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30046B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30046B\"></sup> about Christ and be taken forward to maturity, not laying again the foundation of repentance from acts that lead to death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30046C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30046C\"></sup> and of faith in God,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>instruction about cleansing rites,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30047D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30047D\"></sup> the laying on of hands,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30047E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30047E\"></sup> the resurrection of the dead,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30047F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30047F\"></sup> and eternal judgment.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And God permitting,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30048G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30048G\"></sup> we will do so.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>It is impossible for those who have once been enlightened,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30049H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30049H\"></sup> who have tasted the heavenly gift,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30049I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30049I\"></sup> who have shared in the Holy Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30049J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30049J\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>who have tasted the goodness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30050K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30050K\"></sup> of the word of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30050L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30050L\"></sup> and the powers of the coming age",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and who have fallen away, to be brought back to repentance.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30051M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30051M\"></sup> To their loss they are crucifying the Son of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30051N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30051N\"></sup> all over again and subjecting him to public disgrace.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Land that drinks in the rain often falling on it and that produces a crop useful to those for whom it is farmed receives the blessing of God.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But land that produces thorns and thistles is worthless and is in danger of being cursed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30053O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30053O\"></sup> In the end it will be burned.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Even though we speak like this, dear friends,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30054P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30054P\"></sup> we are convinced of better things in your case—the things that have to do with salvation.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>God is not unjust; he will not forget your work and the love you have shown him as you have helped his people and continue to help them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30055Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30055Q\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>We want each of you to show this same diligence to the very end, so that what you hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30056R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30056R\"></sup> for may be fully realized.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>We do not want you to become lazy, but to imitate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30057S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30057S\"></sup> those who through faith and patience<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30057T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30057T\"></sup> inherit what has been promised.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30057U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30057U\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When God made his promise to Abraham, since there was no one greater for him to swear by, he swore by himself,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30058V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30058V\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>saying, “I will surely bless you and give you many descendants.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30059W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30059W\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And so after waiting patiently, Abraham received what was promised.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30060X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30060X\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>People swear by someone greater than themselves, and the oath confirms what is said and puts an end to all argument.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30061Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30061Y\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Because God wanted to make the unchanging<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30062Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30062Z\"></sup> nature of his purpose very clear to the heirs of what was promised,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30062AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30062AA\"></sup> he confirmed it with an oath.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>God did this so that, by two unchangeable things in which it is impossible for God to lie,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30063AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30063AB\"></sup> we who have fled to take hold of the hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30063AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30063AC\"></sup> set before us may be greatly encouraged.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>We have this hope as an anchor for the soul, firm and secure. It enters the inner sanctuary behind the curtain,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30064AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30064AD\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>where our forerunner, Jesus, has entered on our behalf.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30065AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30065AE\"></sup> He has become a high priest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30065AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30065AF\"></sup> forever, in the order of Melchizedek.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30065AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30065AG\"></sup>"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>This Melchizedek was king of Salem<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30066A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30066A\"></sup> and priest of God Most High.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30066B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30066B\"></sup> He met Abraham returning from the defeat of the kings and blessed him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30066C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30066C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and Abraham gave him a tenth of everything. First, the name Melchizedek means “king of righteousness”; then also, “king of Salem” means “king of peace.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Without father or mother, without genealogy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30068D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30068D\"></sup> without beginning of days or end of life, resembling the Son of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30068E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30068E\"></sup> he remains a priest forever.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Just think how great he was: Even the patriarch<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30069F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30069F\"></sup> Abraham gave him a tenth of the plunder!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30069G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30069G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Now the law requires the descendants of Levi who become priests to collect a tenth from the people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30070H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30070H\"></sup>—that is, from their fellow Israelites—even though they also are descended from Abraham.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>This man, however, did not trace his descent from Levi, yet he collected a tenth from Abraham and blessed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30071I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30071I\"></sup> him who had the promises.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30071J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30071J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And without doubt the lesser is blessed by the greater.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>In the one case, the tenth is collected by people who die; but in the other case, by him who is declared to be living.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30073K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30073K\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>One might even say that Levi, who collects the tenth, paid the tenth through Abraham,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>because when Melchizedek met Abraham, Levi was still in the body of his ancestor.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>If perfection could have been attained through the Levitical priesthood—and indeed the law given to the people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30076L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30076L\"></sup> established that priesthood—why was there still need for another priest to come,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30076M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30076M\"></sup> one in the order of Melchizedek,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30076N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30076N\"></sup> not in the order of Aaron?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For when the priesthood is changed, the law must be changed also.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He of whom these things are said belonged to a different tribe,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30078O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30078O\"></sup> and no one from that tribe has ever served at the altar.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30078P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30078P\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For it is clear that our Lord descended from Judah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30079Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30079Q\"></sup> and in regard to that tribe Moses said nothing about priests.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And what we have said is even more clear if another priest like Melchizedek appears,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>one who has become a priest not on the basis of a regulation as to his ancestry but on the basis of the power of an indestructible life.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For it is declared:“You are a priest forever,in the order of Melchizedek.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30082R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30082R\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The former regulation is set aside because it was weak and useless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30083S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30083S\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>(for the law made nothing perfect),<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30084T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30084T\"></sup> and a better hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30084U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30084U\"></sup> is introduced, by which we draw near to God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30084V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30084V\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And it was not without an oath! Others became priests without any oath,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>but he became a priest with an oath when God said to him:“The Lord has swornand will not change his mind:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30086W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30086W\"></sup>‘You are a priest forever.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30086X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30086X\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Because of this oath, Jesus has become the guarantor of a better covenant.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30087Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30087Y\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Now there have been many of those priests, since death prevented them from continuing in office;",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>but because Jesus lives forever, he has a permanent priesthood.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30089Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30089Z\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Therefore he is able to save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30090AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30090AA\"></sup> completely those who come to God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30090AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30090AB\"></sup> through him, because he always lives to intercede for them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30090AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30090AC\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Such a high priest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30091AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30091AD\"></sup> truly meets our need—one who is holy, blameless, pure, set apart from sinners,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30091AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30091AE\"></sup> exalted above the heavens.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30091AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30091AF\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Unlike the other high priests, he does not need to offer sacrifices<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30092AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30092AG\"></sup> day after day, first for his own sins,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30092AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30092AH\"></sup> and then for the sins of the people. He sacrificed for their sins once for all<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30092AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30092AI\"></sup> when he offered himself.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30092AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30092AJ\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>For the law appoints as high priests men in all their weakness;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30093AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30093AK\"></sup> but the oath, which came after the law, appointed the Son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30093AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30093AL\"></sup> who has been made perfect<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30093AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30093AM\"></sup> forever."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Now the main point of what we are saying is this: We do have such a high priest,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30094A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30094A\"></sup> who sat down at the right hand of the throne of the Majesty in heaven,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30094B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30094B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and who serves in the sanctuary, the true tabernacle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30095C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30095C\"></sup> set up by the Lord, not by a mere human being.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Every high priest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30096D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30096D\"></sup> is appointed to offer both gifts and sacrifices,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30096E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30096E\"></sup> and so it was necessary for this one also to have something to offer.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30096F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30096F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>If he were on earth, he would not be a priest, for there are already priests who offer the gifts prescribed by the law.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30097G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30097G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They serve at a sanctuary that is a copy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30098H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30098H\"></sup> and shadow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30098I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30098I\"></sup> of what is in heaven. This is why Moses was warned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30098J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30098J\"></sup> when he was about to build the tabernacle: “See to it that you make everything according to the pattern shown you on the mountain.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30098K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30098K\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But in fact the ministry Jesus has received is as superior to theirs as the covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30099L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30099L\"></sup> of which he is mediator<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30099M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30099M\"></sup> is superior to the old one, since the new covenant is established on better promises.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For if there had been nothing wrong with that first covenant, no place would have been sought for another.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30100N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30100N\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But God found fault with the people and said:“The days are coming, declares the Lord,when I will make a new covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30101O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30101O\"></sup>with the people of Israeland with the people of Judah.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>It will not be like the covenantI made with their ancestors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30102P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30102P\"></sup>when I took them by the handto lead them out of Egypt,because they did not remain faithful to my covenant,and I turned away from them,declares the Lord.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>This is the covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30103Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30103Q\"></sup> I will establish with the people of Israelafter that time, declares the Lord.I will put my laws in their mindsand write them on their hearts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30103R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30103R\"></sup>I will be their God,and they will be my people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30103S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30103S\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>No longer will they teach their neighbor,or say to one another, ‘Know the Lord,’because they will all know me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30104T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30104T\"></sup>from the least of them to the greatest.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For I will forgive their wickednessand will remember their sins no more.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30105U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30105U\"></sup>”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30105V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30105V\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>By calling this covenant “new,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30106W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30106W\"></sup> he has made the first one obsolete;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30106X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30106X\"></sup> and what is obsolete and outdated will soon disappear."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>Now the first covenant had regulations for worship and also an earthly sanctuary.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30107A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30107A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>A tabernacle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30108B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30108B\"></sup> was set up. In its first room were the lampstand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30108C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30108C\"></sup> and the table<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30108D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30108D\"></sup> with its consecrated bread;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30108E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30108E\"></sup> this was called the Holy Place.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30108F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30108F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Behind the second curtain was a room called the Most Holy Place,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30109G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30109G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>which had the golden altar of incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30110H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30110H\"></sup> and the gold-covered ark of the covenant.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30110I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30110I\"></sup> This ark contained the gold jar of manna,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30110J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30110J\"></sup> Aaron’s staff that had budded,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30110K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30110K\"></sup> and the stone tablets of the covenant.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30110L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30110L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Above the ark were the cherubim of the Glory,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30111M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30111M\"></sup> overshadowing the atonement cover.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30111N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30111N\"></sup> But we cannot discuss these things in detail now.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When everything had been arranged like this, the priests entered regularly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30112O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30112O\"></sup> into the outer room to carry on their ministry.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But only the high priest entered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30113P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30113P\"></sup> the inner room,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30113Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30113Q\"></sup> and that only once a year,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30113R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30113R\"></sup> and never without blood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30113S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30113S\"></sup> which he offered for himself<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30113T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30113T\"></sup> and for the sins the people had committed in ignorance.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30113U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30113U\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The Holy Spirit was showing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30114V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30114V\"></sup> by this that the way<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30114W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30114W\"></sup> into the Most Holy Place had not yet been disclosed as long as the first tabernacle was still functioning.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>This is an illustration<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30115X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30115X\"></sup> for the present time, indicating that the gifts and sacrifices being offered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30115Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30115Y\"></sup> were not able to clear the conscience<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30115Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30115Z\"></sup> of the worshiper.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They are only a matter of food<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30116AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30116AA\"></sup> and drink<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30116AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30116AB\"></sup> and various ceremonial washings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30116AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30116AC\"></sup>—external regulations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30116AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30116AD\"></sup> applying until the time of the new order.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But when Christ came as high priest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30117AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30117AE\"></sup> of the good things that are now already here,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30117AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30117AF\"></sup> he went through the greater and more perfect tabernacle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30117AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30117AG\"></sup> that is not made with human hands,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30117AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30117AH\"></sup> that is to say, is not a part of this creation.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He did not enter by means of the blood of goats and calves;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30118AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30118AI\"></sup> but he entered the Most Holy Place<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30118AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30118AJ\"></sup> once for all<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30118AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30118AK\"></sup> by his own blood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30118AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30118AL\"></sup> thus obtaining eternal redemption.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The blood of goats and bulls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30119AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30119AM\"></sup> and the ashes of a heifer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30119AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30119AN\"></sup> sprinkled on those who are ceremonially unclean sanctify them so that they are outwardly clean.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>How much more, then, will the blood of Christ, who through the eternal Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30120AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30120AO\"></sup> offered himself<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30120AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30120AP\"></sup> unblemished to God, cleanse our consciences<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30120AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30120AQ\"></sup> from acts that lead to death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30120AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30120AR\"></sup> so that we may serve the living God!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30120AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30120AS\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For this reason Christ is the mediator<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30121AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30121AT\"></sup> of a new covenant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30121AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30121AU\"></sup> that those who are called<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30121AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30121AV\"></sup> may receive the promised<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30121AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30121AW\"></sup> eternal inheritance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30121AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30121AX\"></sup>—now that he has died as a ransom to set them free from the sins committed under the first covenant.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30121AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30121AY\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>In the case of a will, it is necessary to prove the death of the one who made it,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>because a will is in force only when somebody has died; it never takes effect while the one who made it is living.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>This is why even the first covenant was not put into effect without blood.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30124AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30124AZ\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>When Moses had proclaimed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30125BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30125BA\"></sup> every command of the law to all the people, he took the blood of calves,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30125BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30125BB\"></sup> together with water, scarlet wool and branches of hyssop, and sprinkled the scroll and all the people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30125BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30125BC\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>He said, “This is the blood of the covenant, which God has commanded you to keep.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30126BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30126BD\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>In the same way, he sprinkled with the blood both the tabernacle and everything used in its ceremonies.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>In fact, the law requires that nearly everything be cleansed with blood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30128BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30128BE\"></sup> and without the shedding of blood there is no forgiveness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30128BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30128BF\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>It was necessary, then, for the copies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30129BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30129BG\"></sup> of the heavenly things to be purified with these sacrifices, but the heavenly things themselves with better sacrifices than these.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For Christ did not enter a sanctuary made with human hands that was only a copy of the true one;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30130BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30130BH\"></sup> he entered heaven itself,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30130BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30130BI\"></sup> now to appear for us in God’s presence.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30130BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30130BJ\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Nor did he enter heaven to offer himself again and again, the way the high priest enters the Most Holy Place<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30131BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30131BK\"></sup> every year with blood that is not his own.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30131BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30131BL\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Otherwise Christ would have had to suffer many times since the creation of the world.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30132BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30132BM\"></sup> But he has appeared<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30132BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30132BN\"></sup> once for all<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30132BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30132BO\"></sup> at the culmination of the ages to do away with sin by the sacrifice of himself.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30132BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30132BP\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Just as people are destined to die once,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30133BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30133BQ\"></sup> and after that to face judgment,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30133BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30133BR\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>so Christ was sacrificed once<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30134BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30134BS\"></sup> to take away the sins of many; and he will appear a second time,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30134BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30134BT\"></sup> not to bear sin,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30134BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30134BU\"></sup> but to bring salvation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30134BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30134BV\"></sup> to those who are waiting for him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30134BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30134BW\"></sup>"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>The law is only a shadow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30135A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30135A\"></sup> of the good things<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30135B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30135B\"></sup> that are coming—not the realities themselves.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30135C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30135C\"></sup> For this reason it can never, by the same sacrifices repeated endlessly year after year, make perfect<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30135D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30135D\"></sup> those who draw near to worship.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30135E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30135E\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Otherwise, would they not have stopped being offered? For the worshipers would have been cleansed once for all, and would no longer have felt guilty for their sins.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30136F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30136F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But those sacrifices are an annual reminder of sins.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30137G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30137G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>It is impossible for the blood of bulls and goats<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30138H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30138H\"></sup> to take away sins.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30138I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30138I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Therefore, when Christ came into the world,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30139J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30139J\"></sup> he said:“Sacrifice and offering you did not desire,but a body you prepared for me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30139K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30139K\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>with burnt offerings and sin offeringsyou were not pleased.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then I said, ‘Here I am—it is written about me in the scroll<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30141L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30141L\"></sup>—I have come to do your will, my God.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30141M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30141M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>First he said, “Sacrifices and offerings, burnt offerings and sin offerings you did not desire, nor were you pleased with them”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30142N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30142N\"></sup>—though they were offered in accordance with the law.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then he said, “Here I am, I have come to do your will.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30143O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30143O\"></sup> He sets aside the first to establish the second.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And by that will, we have been made holy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30144P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30144P\"></sup> through the sacrifice of the body<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30144Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30144Q\"></sup> of Jesus Christ once for all.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30144R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30144R\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Day after day every priest stands and performs his religious duties; again and again he offers the same sacrifices,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30145S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30145S\"></sup> which can never take away sins.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30145T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30145T\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But when this priest had offered for all time one sacrifice for sins,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30146U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30146U\"></sup> he sat down at the right hand of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30146V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30146V\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and since that time he waits for his enemies to be made his footstool.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30147W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30147W\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For by one sacrifice he has made perfect<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30148X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30148X\"></sup> forever those who are being made holy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30148Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30148Y\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The Holy Spirit also testifies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30149Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30149Z\"></sup> to us about this. First he says:",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“This is the covenant I will make with themafter that time, says the Lord.I will put my laws in their hearts,and I will write them on their minds.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30150AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30150AA\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then he adds:“Their sins and lawless actsI will remember no more.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30151AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30151AB\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And where these have been forgiven, sacrifice for sin is no longer necessary.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Therefore, brothers and sisters, since we have confidence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30153AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30153AC\"></sup> to enter the Most Holy Place<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30153AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30153AD\"></sup> by the blood of Jesus,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>by a new and living way<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30154AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30154AE\"></sup> opened for us through the curtain,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30154AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30154AF\"></sup> that is, his body,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>and since we have a great priest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30155AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30155AG\"></sup> over the house of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30155AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30155AH\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>let us draw near to God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30156AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30156AI\"></sup> with a sincere heart and with the full assurance that faith brings,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30156AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30156AJ\"></sup> having our hearts sprinkled to cleanse us from a guilty conscience<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30156AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30156AK\"></sup> and having our bodies washed with pure water.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30156AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30156AL\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Let us hold unswervingly to the hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30157AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30157AM\"></sup> we profess,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30157AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30157AN\"></sup> for he who promised is faithful.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30157AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30157AO\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And let us consider how we may spur one another on toward love and good deeds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30158AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30158AP\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>not giving up meeting together,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30159AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30159AQ\"></sup> as some are in the habit of doing, but encouraging one another<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30159AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30159AR\"></sup>—and all the more as you see the Day approaching.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30159AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30159AS\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>If we deliberately keep on sinning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30160AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30160AT\"></sup> after we have received the knowledge of the truth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30160AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30160AU\"></sup> no sacrifice for sins is left,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>but only a fearful expectation of judgment and of raging fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30161AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30161AV\"></sup> that will consume the enemies of God.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Anyone who rejected the law of Moses died without mercy on the testimony of two or three witnesses.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30162AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30162AW\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>How much more severely do you think someone deserves to be punished who has trampled the Son of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30163AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30163AX\"></sup> underfoot,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30163AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30163AY\"></sup> who has treated as an unholy thing the blood of the covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30163AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30163AZ\"></sup> that sanctified them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30163BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30163BA\"></sup> and who has insulted the Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30163BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30163BB\"></sup> of grace?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30163BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30163BC\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>For we know him who said, “It is mine to avenge; I will repay,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30164BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30164BD\"></sup> and again, “The Lord will judge his people.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30164BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30164BE\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>It is a dreadful thing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30165BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30165BF\"></sup> to fall into the hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30165BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30165BG\"></sup> of the living God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30165BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30165BH\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Remember those earlier days after you had received the light,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30166BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30166BI\"></sup> when you endured in a great conflict full of suffering.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30166BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30166BJ\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Sometimes you were publicly exposed to insult and persecution;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30167BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30167BK\"></sup> at other times you stood side by side with those who were so treated.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30167BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30167BL\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>You suffered along with those in prison<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30168BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30168BM\"></sup> and joyfully accepted the confiscation of your property, because you knew that you yourselves had better and lasting possessions.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30168BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30168BN\"></sup>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>So do not throw away your confidence;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30169BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30169BO\"></sup> it will be richly rewarded.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>You need to persevere<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30170BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30170BP\"></sup> so that when you have done the will of God, you will receive what he has promised.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30170BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30170BQ\"></sup>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>For,“In just a little while,he who is coming<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30171BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30171BR\"></sup> will comeand will not delay.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30171BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30171BS\"></sup>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And,“But my righteous one will live by faith.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30172BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30172BT\"></sup>And I take no pleasurein the one who shrinks back.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30172BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30172BU\"></sup>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>But we do not belong to those who shrink back and are destroyed, but to those who have faith and are saved."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>Now faith is confidence in what we hope for<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30174A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30174A\"></sup> and assurance about what we do not see.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30174B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30174B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>This is what the ancients were commended for.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30175C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30175C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>By faith we understand that the universe was formed at God’s command,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30176D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30176D\"></sup> so that what is seen was not made out of what was visible.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>By faith Abel brought God a better offering than Cain did. By faith he was commended<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30177E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30177E\"></sup> as righteous, when God spoke well of his offerings.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30177F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30177F\"></sup> And by faith Abel still speaks, even though he is dead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30177G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30177G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>By faith Enoch was taken from this life, so that he did not experience death: “He could not be found, because God had taken him away.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30178H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30178H\"></sup> For before he was taken, he was commended as one who pleased God.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And without faith it is impossible to please God, because anyone who comes to him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30179I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30179I\"></sup> must believe that he exists and that he rewards those who earnestly seek him.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>By faith Noah, when warned about things not yet seen,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30180J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30180J\"></sup> in holy fear built an ark<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30180K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30180K\"></sup> to save his family.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30180L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30180L\"></sup> By his faith he condemned the world and became heir of the righteousness that is in keeping with faith.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30180M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30180M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>By faith Abraham, when called to go to a place he would later receive as his inheritance,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30181N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30181N\"></sup> obeyed and went,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30181O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30181O\"></sup> even though he did not know where he was going.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>By faith he made his home in the promised land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30182P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30182P\"></sup> like a stranger in a foreign country; he lived in tents,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30182Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30182Q\"></sup> as did Isaac and Jacob, who were heirs with him of the same promise.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30182R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30182R\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For he was looking forward to the city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30183S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30183S\"></sup> with foundations,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30183T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30183T\"></sup> whose architect and builder is God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30183U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30183U\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And by faith even Sarah, who was past childbearing age,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30184V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30184V\"></sup> was enabled to bear children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30184W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30184W\"></sup> because she considered him faithful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30184X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30184X\"></sup> who had made the promise.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And so from this one man, and he as good as dead,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30185Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30185Y\"></sup> came descendants as numerous as the stars in the sky and as countless as the sand on the seashore.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30185Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30185Z\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>All these people were still living by faith when they died. They did not receive the things promised;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30186AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30186AA\"></sup> they only saw them and welcomed them from a distance,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30186AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30186AB\"></sup> admitting that they were foreigners and strangers on earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30186AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30186AC\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>People who say such things show that they are looking for a country of their own.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>If they had been thinking of the country they had left, they would have had opportunity to return.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30188AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30188AD\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Instead, they were longing for a better country—a heavenly one.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30189AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30189AE\"></sup> Therefore God is not ashamed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30189AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30189AF\"></sup> to be called their God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30189AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30189AG\"></sup> for he has prepared a city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30189AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30189AH\"></sup> for them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>By faith Abraham, when God tested him, offered Isaac as a sacrifice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30190AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30190AI\"></sup> He who had embraced the promises was about to sacrifice his one and only son,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>even though God had said to him, “It is through Isaac that your offspring will be reckoned.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30191AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30191AJ\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Abraham reasoned that God could even raise the dead,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30192AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30192AK\"></sup> and so in a manner of speaking he did receive Isaac back from death.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>By faith Isaac blessed Jacob and Esau in regard to their future.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30193AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30193AL\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>By faith Jacob, when he was dying, blessed each of Joseph’s sons,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30194AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30194AM\"></sup> and worshiped as he leaned on the top of his staff.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>By faith Joseph, when his end was near, spoke about the exodus of the Israelites from Egypt and gave instructions concerning the burial of his bones.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30195AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30195AN\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>By faith Moses’ parents hid him for three months after he was born,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30196AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30196AO\"></sup> because they saw he was no ordinary child, and they were not afraid of the king’s edict.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30196AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30196AP\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>By faith Moses, when he had grown up, refused to be known as the son of Pharaoh’s daughter.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30197AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30197AQ\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>He chose to be mistreated<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30198AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30198AR\"></sup> along with the people of God rather than to enjoy the fleeting pleasures of sin.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>He regarded disgrace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30199AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30199AS\"></sup> for the sake of Christ<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30199AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30199AT\"></sup> as of greater value than the treasures of Egypt, because he was looking ahead to his reward.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30199AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30199AU\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>By faith he left Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30200AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30200AV\"></sup> not fearing the king’s anger; he persevered because he saw him who is invisible.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>By faith he kept the Passover and the application of blood, so that the destroyer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30201AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30201AW\"></sup> of the firstborn would not touch the firstborn of Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30201AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30201AX\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>By faith the people passed through the Red Sea as on dry land; but when the Egyptians tried to do so, they were drowned.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30202AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30202AY\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>By faith the walls of Jericho fell, after the army had marched around them for seven days.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30203AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30203AZ\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>By faith the prostitute Rahab, because she welcomed the spies, was not killed with those who were disobedient.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30204BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30204BA\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And what more shall I say? I do not have time to tell about Gideon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30205BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30205BB\"></sup> Barak,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30205BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30205BC\"></sup> Samson<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30205BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30205BD\"></sup> and Jephthah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30205BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30205BE\"></sup> about David<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30205BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30205BF\"></sup> and Samuel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30205BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30205BG\"></sup> and the prophets,",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>who through faith conquered kingdoms,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30206BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30206BH\"></sup> administered justice, and gained what was promised; who shut the mouths of lions,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30206BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30206BI\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>quenched the fury of the flames,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30207BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30207BJ\"></sup> and escaped the edge of the sword;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30207BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30207BK\"></sup> whose weakness was turned to strength;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30207BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30207BL\"></sup> and who became powerful in battle and routed foreign armies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30207BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30207BM\"></sup>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Women received back their dead, raised to life again.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30208BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30208BN\"></sup> There were others who were tortured, refusing to be released so that they might gain an even better resurrection.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Some faced jeers and flogging,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30209BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30209BO\"></sup> and even chains and imprisonment.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30209BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30209BP\"></sup>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>They were put to death by stoning;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30210BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30210BQ\"></sup> they were sawed in two; they were killed by the sword.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30210BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30210BR\"></sup> They went about in sheepskins and goatskins,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30210BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30210BS\"></sup> destitute, persecuted and mistreated—",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>the world was not worthy of them. They wandered in deserts and mountains, living in caves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30211BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30211BT\"></sup> and in holes in the ground.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>These were all commended<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30212BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30212BU\"></sup> for their faith, yet none of them received what had been promised,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30212BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30212BV\"></sup>",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>since God had planned something better for us so that only together with us<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30213BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30213BW\"></sup> would they be made perfect.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30213BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30213BX\"></sup>"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>Therefore, since we are surrounded by such a great cloud of witnesses, let us throw off everything that hinders and the sin that so easily entangles. And let us run<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30214A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30214A\"></sup> with perseverance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30214B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30214B\"></sup> the race marked out for us,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>fixing our eyes on Jesus,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30215C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30215C\"></sup> the pioneer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30215D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30215D\"></sup> and perfecter of faith. For the joy set before him he endured the cross,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30215E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30215E\"></sup> scorning its shame,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30215F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30215F\"></sup> and sat down at the right hand of the throne of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30215G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30215G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Consider him who endured such opposition from sinners, so that you will not grow weary<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30216H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30216H\"></sup> and lose heart.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>In your struggle against sin, you have not yet resisted to the point of shedding your blood.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30217I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30217I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And have you completely forgotten this word of encouragement that addresses you as a father addresses his son? It says,“My son, do not make light of the Lord’s discipline,and do not lose heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30218J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30218J\"></sup> when he rebukes you,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>because the Lord disciplines the one he loves,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30219K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30219K\"></sup>and he chastens everyone he accepts as his son.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30219L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30219L\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Endure hardship as discipline; God is treating you as his children.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30220M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30220M\"></sup> For what children are not disciplined by their father?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>If you are not disciplined—and everyone undergoes discipline<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30221N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30221N\"></sup>—then you are not legitimate, not true sons and daughters at all.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Moreover, we have all had human fathers who disciplined us and we respected them for it. How much more should we submit to the Father of spirits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30222O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30222O\"></sup> and live!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30222P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30222P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They disciplined us for a little while as they thought best; but God disciplines us for our good, in order that we may share in his holiness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30223Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30223Q\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>No discipline seems pleasant at the time, but painful. Later on, however, it produces a harvest of righteousness and peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30224R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30224R\"></sup> for those who have been trained by it.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore, strengthen your feeble arms and weak knees.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30225S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30225S\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Make level paths for your feet,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30226T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30226T\"></sup> so that the lame may not be disabled, but rather healed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30226U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30226U\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Make every effort to live in peace with everyone<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30227V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30227V\"></sup> and to be holy;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30227W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30227W\"></sup> without holiness no one will see the Lord.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30227X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30227X\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>See to it that no one falls short of the grace of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30228Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30228Y\"></sup> and that no bitter root<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30228Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30228Z\"></sup> grows up to cause trouble and defile many.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>See that no one is sexually immoral,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30229AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30229AA\"></sup> or is godless like Esau, who for a single meal sold his inheritance rights as the oldest son.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30229AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30229AB\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Afterward, as you know, when he wanted to inherit this blessing, he was rejected. Even though he sought the blessing with tears,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30230AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30230AC\"></sup> he could not change what he had done.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>You have not come to a mountain that can be touched and that is burning with fire; to darkness, gloom and storm;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30231AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30231AD\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>to a trumpet blast<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30232AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30232AE\"></sup> or to such a voice speaking words<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30232AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30232AF\"></sup> that those who heard it begged that no further word be spoken to them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30232AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30232AG\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>because they could not bear what was commanded: “If even an animal touches the mountain, it must be stoned to death.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30233AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30233AH\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The sight was so terrifying that Moses said, “I am trembling with fear.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30234AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30234AI\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But you have come to Mount Zion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30235AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30235AJ\"></sup> to the city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30235AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30235AK\"></sup> of the living God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30235AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30235AL\"></sup> the heavenly Jerusalem.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30235AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30235AM\"></sup> You have come to thousands upon thousands of angels in joyful assembly,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>to the church of the firstborn,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30236AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30236AN\"></sup> whose names are written in heaven.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30236AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30236AO\"></sup> You have come to God, the Judge of all,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30236AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30236AP\"></sup> to the spirits of the righteous made perfect,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30236AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30236AQ\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>to Jesus the mediator<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30237AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30237AR\"></sup> of a new covenant, and to the sprinkled blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30237AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30237AS\"></sup> that speaks a better word than the blood of Abel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30237AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30237AT\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>See to it that you do not refuse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30238AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30238AU\"></sup> him who speaks.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30238AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30238AV\"></sup> If they did not escape when they refused him who warned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30238AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30238AW\"></sup> them on earth, how much less will we, if we turn away from him who warns us from heaven?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30238AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30238AX\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>At that time his voice shook the earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30239AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30239AY\"></sup> but now he has promised, “Once more I will shake not only the earth but also the heavens.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30239AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30239AZ\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The words “once more” indicate the removing of what can be shaken<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30240BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30240BA\"></sup>—that is, created things—so that what cannot be shaken may remain.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Therefore, since we are receiving a kingdom that cannot be shaken,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30241BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30241BB\"></sup> let us be thankful, and so worship God acceptably with reverence and awe,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30241BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30241BC\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>for our “God is a consuming fire.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30242BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30242BD\"></sup>"
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>Keep on loving one another as brothers and sisters.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30243A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30243A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Do not forget to show hospitality to strangers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30244B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30244B\"></sup> for by so doing some people have shown hospitality to angels without knowing it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30244C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30244C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Continue to remember those in prison<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30245D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30245D\"></sup> as if you were together with them in prison, and those who are mistreated as if you yourselves were suffering.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Marriage should be honored by all,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30246E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30246E\"></sup> and the marriage bed kept pure, for God will judge the adulterer and all the sexually immoral.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30246F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30246F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Keep your lives free from the love of money<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30247G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30247G\"></sup> and be content with what you have,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30247H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30247H\"></sup> because God has said,“Never will I leave you;never will I forsake you.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30247I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30247I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So we say with confidence,“The Lord is my helper; I will not be afraid.What can mere mortals do to me?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30248J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30248J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Remember your leaders,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30249K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30249K\"></sup> who spoke the word of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30249L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30249L\"></sup> to you. Consider the outcome of their way of life and imitate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30249M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30249M\"></sup> their faith.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Jesus Christ is the same yesterday and today and forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30250N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30250N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Do not be carried away by all kinds of strange teachings.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30251O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30251O\"></sup> It is good for our hearts to be strengthened<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30251P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30251P\"></sup> by grace, not by eating ceremonial foods,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30251Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30251Q\"></sup> which is of no benefit to those who do so.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30251R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30251R\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>We have an altar from which those who minister at the tabernacle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30252S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30252S\"></sup> have no right to eat.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30252T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30252T\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The high priest carries the blood of animals into the Most Holy Place as a sin offering,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30253U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30253U\"></sup> but the bodies are burned outside the camp.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30253V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30253V\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And so Jesus also suffered outside the city gate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30254W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30254W\"></sup> to make the people holy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30254X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30254X\"></sup> through his own blood.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30254Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30254Y\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Let us, then, go to him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30255Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30255Z\"></sup> outside the camp, bearing the disgrace he bore.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30255AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30255AA\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For here we do not have an enduring city,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30256AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30256AB\"></sup> but we are looking for the city that is to come.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30256AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30256AC\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Through Jesus, therefore, let us continually offer to God a sacrifice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30257AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30257AD\"></sup> of praise—the fruit of lips<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30257AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30257AE\"></sup> that openly profess his name.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And do not forget to do good and to share with others,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30258AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30258AF\"></sup> for with such sacrifices<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30258AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30258AG\"></sup> God is pleased.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Have confidence in your leaders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30259AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30259AH\"></sup> and submit to their authority, because they keep watch over you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30259AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30259AI\"></sup> as those who must give an account. Do this so that their work will be a joy, not a burden, for that would be of no benefit to you.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Pray for us.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30260AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30260AJ\"></sup> We are sure that we have a clear conscience<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30260AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30260AK\"></sup> and desire to live honorably in every way.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>I particularly urge you to pray so that I may be restored to you soon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30261AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30261AL\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Now may the God of peace,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30262AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30262AM\"></sup> who through the blood of the eternal covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30262AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30262AN\"></sup> brought back from the dead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30262AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30262AO\"></sup> our Lord Jesus, that great Shepherd of the sheep,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30262AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30262AP\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>equip you with everything good for doing his will,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30263AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30263AQ\"></sup> and may he work in us<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30263AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30263AR\"></sup> what is pleasing to him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30263AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30263AS\"></sup> through Jesus Christ, to whom be glory for ever and ever. Amen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30263AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30263AT\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Brothers and sisters, I urge you to bear with my word of exhortation, for in fact I have written to you quite briefly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30264AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30264AU\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>I want you to know that our brother Timothy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30265AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30265AV\"></sup> has been released. If he arrives soon, I will come with him to see you.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Greet all your leaders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30266AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30266AW\"></sup> and all the Lord’s people. Those from Italy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30266AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30266AX\"></sup> send you their greetings.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Grace be with you all.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30267AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30267AY\"></sup>"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;